@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<div class="jumbotron" style="color:orange;">
    <h1>Disaster Relief Foundation</h1>
    <p   class="lead">As the Disaster Relief Foundation ,we aims to provide humanitarian assistance and support to communities and individuals affected by disasters, emergencies, and crises</p>
    
</div>



<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4" style="background-color: mediumpurple;">
        <h2>GoodsDonation</h2>
        <p>
            These are the ways in which we wish to contribute goods in our community , anyone is welcome to 
            donate goods that they might not have a use for and would like to share a bit of kindness
            we accept all kinds of Goods from Clothing , non-perishable foods ..
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" @Html.ActionLink("List of Goods Donated", "Index", "GoodsDonations")></a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Money Donation</h2>
        <p>Money Donations go a long way in assisting . it gives the foundation the power to go out and do more 
           it allows us to really look into what we lack and get it for the people suffering these criseses 
           we accept all amounts no amount is too small
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" @Html.ActionLink("List of Amount Donated", "Index", "MonetaryDonations")> </a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4" style="background-color: mediumpurple;">
        <h2>Disasters</h2>
        <p>Our donations don't just reach out to the disasters that we are aware of , these can be even for the 
           disasters that a donor might know of and want to record the disaster on our system so that they can
           record these events for others to record'</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" @Html.ActionLink("List of Disaster Occured", "Index", "Disasters")> </a></p>
    </div>
</div>